So at the top, you're going
to see the same quick access

00:11:01.180 --> 00:11:02.650
to search that you used to.

00:11:02.650 --> 00:11:04.840
And below that, we're
introducing a favorites row

00:11:04.840 --> 00:11:07.600
for favorite apps to easily
launch into the favorite apps

00:11:07.600 --> 00:11:09.310
right from the
top of the screen.

