We have code labs,
you can actually go in

00:34:55.469 --> 00:34:58.350
and build your own TV app.

00:34:58.350 --> 00:35:00.570
And you can come to the
office hours, I'll be there

00:35:00.570 --> 00:35:03.270
and you can ask questions
or you can go online

00:35:03.270 --> 00:35:04.552
